rComments: Hilmi is a caring prof who knows what he's talking about and his clear lectures show that. He marks pretty fairly and the assessments aren't a surprise if you know how to do the problems in the course. Final exam was slightly tougher than the midterm but still fair overall.

74% of my grade relied on exams or tests, so if you are not a great test-taker, I do not recommend this prof! Although... prof Dajani was very clear about the course expectations, is a super nice guy, and is a very clear lecturer. I would definitely take a course with him again!
